title: A Keynote: Traffic & Conversion Summit 2016
description: Such a great event filled with a lot of my homies from throughout the years. We talk a lot about internet marketing and current shifts in today's digital and technology landscapes. A lot of fun here. Definitely worth the listen if you're looking to take your online game to new heights.
